snippet: Maj. Gen. Michael Carey, who oversees the nation’s arsenal of intercontinental missiles, was fired on Friday for personal misbehavior, the Air Force said.
abstract: Maj Gen Michael Carey, who oversees the nation’s arsenal of intercontinental missiles, is fired for personal misbehavior; Air Force does not say what he did wrong but provides a list of things he was not being accused of, including sexual misconduct.
lead_paragraph: Maj. Gen. Michael Carey, who oversees the nation’s arsenal of intercontinental missiles, was fired on Friday for personal misbehavior, the Air Force said.
